    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "下手甲",
        "二夫人",
        "四下手",
        "姜永志",
        "展昭",
        "探子",
        "欧阳春",
        "蒋平",
        "邓车"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、邓车同上。〖点绛唇〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相貌堂堂胆包天，全凭袖箭镇江南。结交天下英雄汉，坐地分赃乐安然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，邓车。霸占邓家堡，倒也逍遥自在。我有一好友，名叫姜永志，去到东京\n偷盗皇家桃花玉马，去有多日，未见归来。\n左右，伺候了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二寨主到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜永志上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟请坐。贤弟一路行来，多受风霜之苦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉马之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已被小弟盗来。大哥请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好马呀，好马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥想必有爱马之意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好马人人皆爱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就奉送大哥。多谢贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜永志望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟看什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不见二位嫂嫂？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，请你家二位主母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "下手甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请二位主母。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二夫人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二夫人",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻听寨主唤，迈步到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位嫂嫂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，看酒伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀寨主：庄外来了许多车辆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待小弟前去走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "些些小事，何劳贤弟，众喽兵出庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、四青袍、欧阳春同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当是谁，原来是欧大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是邓贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请到庄中一叙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要拜庄。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下，同上。欧阳春望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欧大哥，看些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不见二寨主？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请你二寨主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "下手甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请二寨主。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜永志上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟见过欧大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是欧大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久闻大名，如雷贯耳。今日一见，真乃名不虚传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥夸奖了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备得有酒，与大哥畅饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此就要叨扰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，将酒摆下。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻听人言，二寨主曾到东京，盗了皇家桃花玉马，可算英雄好汉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是小弟作了一桩不才之事，何劳大哥称赞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁有旨，曾命包公差人前来拿你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢说包公手下之人，就是天神下界，我姜某何惧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休出狂言，后悔无及。告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不送。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卢方、徐庆、蒋平、白玉堂、展昭同上，欧阳春转回。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "邓车",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥为何去而复转？"
        },
        {
          "character": "欧阳春",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是我去而复转，包公已差人前来拿你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我会他一会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "展昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大花蝴蝶，私盗皇家国宝，该当何罪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得胡言，看镖！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜永志、展昭同起打，八股连环下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒋平",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花蝴蝶甚是厉害，如若败下，必从水道而逃，我不免在鸳鸯桥下等候便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（姜永志上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "姜永志",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！那厮杀法厉害，不免从水道而逃便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（开打。姜永志被擒。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
